{
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , the circuit shown in Fig. 4 is simulated to show the method's effect. In order to show the effectiveness of the method introduced in this paper, some simulation is done using the two methods. The diagnosed results using the method given in [CITATION_2] and this paper for soft fault in R 1 are given in Table 3 . For each faulty state of R 1 , 20 Monte-Carlo analyses are done.",
